page.title: 03A DAY IN THE LIFE OF ANDREW
page.content: 0600 WAKE UP,GET DRESSED AND DO PAPER ROUND.HAVE WASH AND EAT BREAKFAST.WATCH T.V.,WALK TO SCHOOL WITH MY FRIEND.HAVE REGISTRATION. 0900 FIRST LESSON "ENGLISH",READ OR ANSWER QUESTIONS. 1030 WALK DOWN TO LOWER SCHOOL FOR CRICKET. 1215 HAVE PACKED LUNCH AND SIT DOWN AND TALK. 1330 REGISTRATION,THEN MATHS AND DOUBLE HISTORY. 1540 SCHOOL FINISHED.WALK HOME WITH FRIEND.GET HOME,HAVE A SNACK AND OUT FOR A GAME OF FOOTBALL. 1745 HAVE DINNER AND THEN DO THE WIPING UP.PROGRAM VIDEO TO RECORD WHEN I'M OUT PLAYING FOOTBALL. 2045 ARRIVE HOME,HAVE SHOWER.MAKE SANDWICHES FOR NEXT DAY.WATCH T.V.,THEN GO TO BED.
